.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^dir%^RESET%^ - the directory to scan for new files

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/hospital.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the directory to scan for new files. The data directory
stores the configuration files for the hospital that define the zones,
groups and npcs.

